{
  "text": "De Angelis et al., Zhang et al., and Hopkins et al. modeled the energy storage using linear constraints and proposed LP models to optimize energy cost [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] , [CITATION_3] . Arabali et al. proposed a Genetic Algorithm (GA) based optimization method to select the optimal storage capacity for the smart grid [CITATION_4] . Vytelingum et al. proposed a game-theoretic framework to analyze the effect of household storage on the energy price [CITATION_5] .",
